functions of the brain.

00:00:46.430 --> 00:00:50.510 align:middle line:84%
But is consciousness contained
only within our brain?

00:00:50.510 --> 00:00:53.150 align:middle line:84%
Many ancient traditions
thought of the heart

00:00:53.150 --> 00:00:55.910 align:middle line:84%
as the primary seat
of consciousness,

00:00:55.910 --> 00:00:59.513 align:middle line:84%
the key to accessing
our inner wisdom.

