frequency range.

00:18:19.640 --> 00:18:22.550 align:middle line:90%
And how do we achieve that?

00:18:22.550 --> 00:18:27.800 align:middle line:84%
It all comes down to a
certain kind of attitude--

00:18:27.800 --> 00:18:33.530 align:middle line:84%
