of gratitude and compassion.

00:18:33.530 --> 00:18:37.160 align:middle line:84%
Focusing on what we're grateful
for and being compassionate

00:18:37.160 --> 00:18:41.360 align:middle line:84%
influences our system
in powerful ways.

00:18:41.360 --> 00:18:46.010 align:middle line:84%
This really is about what
