00:18:46.010 --> 00:18:49.430 align:middle line:84%
It's about our
attitude towards life.

00:18:49.430 --> 00:18:54.290 align:middle line:84%
Are we in gratitude and focused
on what we're thankful for?

00:18:54.290 --> 00:18:57.410 align:middle line:84%
Or are we focusing on
what's not to our liking

00:18:57.410 --> 00:18:59.780 align:middle line:90%
